metadata.name: Clone Kongz #1
metadata.description: Clone Kongz bring the first step into the SerumLabz Ecosystem. This super Fun collection embodies the Kongz Love of Pop & Retro themes by each being created from amongst 215 layers. As we move through the Mint our Staking will launch and thus when you stake Clone Kongz, they will reward you with $LabTokenZ. Get enough $LabTokenZ and maybe stop by to visit The Scientist once he's done remodeling because he's building something extra special for the clones to have fun with!These Clone Kongz are the best most fashionable version of Kongz yet, with a chill vibe through and through.SerumLabz will continue to show their commitment to building a solid community and offering continued utility, excitement, quality and inspiration through this collection.
